   "We quadrupled our holdings, and now we can offer opportunities
for students that are rare for any film school," said David Litschel,
academic dean of the institute.

   * Activities: Meet NHL players, past and present; cruise on ice,
in-line and street hockey rinks; test shot for speed and accuracy;
have picture taken with Stanley Cup; visit "Coolest Kids Zone";
create own hockey trading card; bid on unique hockey memorabilia, and
more.
